About the map:
This map is a maze i found the idea when I was playing a hand held game were u have to get the ball through the maze I thought that it would be a good CSS map. 

There is 2 spawns CT and T they are on opposite side of the map the aim of the map is it find your way through the maze and kills the opposite team and winning the game. 

This is a big version of my other map caled Aim_XanMaze_Small 

 
This map is my 8th one there will be about 10 maps all together.
